{"TopicId":193435,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Should Scifi Take Itself So Seriously?","CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-27T17:26:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-27T17:26:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think scifi DOES take itself too seriously at times.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am not saying there should be no serious dramatic scifi, what I am saying is that there is a dramatic shortage of lighthearted scifi fare.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot everything needs to be epic, and if you must have heroism, why not include some fun humor into the mix as well?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the movie Sonic for that and... played it... the original game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Kc9lVbz_-_o?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-27T18:30:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrying to recall a real life epic hero looking epic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-28T00:02:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223776904\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588012252\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTrying to recall a real life epic hero looking epic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappens everyday 24/7.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoys and teenagers make\u00A0heroic last stands in sports games all the time, win or lose.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEven I\u00A0used to do this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMany other ways of being heroic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nToo many to mention.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-28T00:05:07Z\u0022 title=\u002204/28/2020 12:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 28, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Spacescifi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-28T01:14:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRed Dwarf\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nHitchhiker\u0027s Guide to the Galaxy\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGalaxy Quest\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGuardians of the Galaxy\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nStargate SG1\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nThose were just off the top of my head. Seems \u0022lighthearted/funny scifi\u0022 is pretty well represented.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-28T01:40:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223777059\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588036474\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n29 minutes ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRed Dwarf\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nHitchhiker\u0027s Guide to the Galaxy\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGalaxy Quest\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGuardians of the Galaxy\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nStargate SG1\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nThose were just off the top of my head. Seems \u0022lighthearted/funny scifi\u0022 is pretty well represented.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRed Dwarf is virtually unknown to many. Americans, certainly unlike the phenomenon of Dr Who.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHitchhiker\u0027s was not very funny to me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGuardians was not very funny either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps having comical yet at the same time competent villains like Jim Carrey\u0027s Eggman is rare.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt certainly seems so.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStargate played things too serious to really be funny, despite Oneil\u0027s attempts, which became boring after a while as were the goauld and other villains being incompetent to the extreme.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeriously. I could have beat SGI myself by saturating the grass around the stargate beforehand with flammable liquid, \u00A0then light it so they cannot run back to the gate nor escape.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWall of fire.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEasy peasy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess I like it when villain\u0027s are hilariously overconfident AND competent. As opposed to being overconfident with zero basis for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMakes their eventual defeat so much more satisfying.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/okpthYwPEnw?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-28T01:44:13Z\u0022 title=\u002204/28/2020 01:44  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 28, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Spacescifi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-28T03:50:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223777033\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588032170\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacescifi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Spacescifi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoys and teenagers make\u00A0heroic last stands in sports games all the time, win or lose.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not a \u0022hero\u0022, it\u0027s just a \u0022show off\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-28T04:19:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223777099\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588045814\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s not a \u0022hero\u0022, it\u0027s just a \u0022show off\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot always. There have been plenty of times I played on underdog teams where I struggled to win... not to show off, but to help them win for once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-28T04:23:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223777110\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022193435\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221588047585\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacescifi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Spacescifi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot always. There have been plenty of times I played on underdog teams where I struggled to win... not to show off, but to help them win for once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat would you loose in case of defeat?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}